{"tid":2171694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"留意健康碼的登門坎效應 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T15:48:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b59d114bbe28e8f30ed752d4e5a43d6fd7a62a80","tid":2171694,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200824/7JALUHDEZJEIRMTTLCTCELQ5AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200824%2F7JALUHDEZJEIRMTTLCTCELQ5AM%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=f7d396c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200824%2F7JALUHDEZJEIRMTTLCTCELQ5AM%2F&h=c47a1812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200824/7JALUHDEZJEIRMTTLCTCELQ5AM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n留意健康碼的登門坎效應 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5BRH3jO1227imkcNu2--BFUorSc=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWERHOD4J5FNVK6LZXWOHCDXQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5BRH3jO1227imkcNu2--BFUorSc%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWERHOD4J5FNVK6LZXWOHCDXQ4.jpg&h=e6003709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有建制派議員吹風，建議政府跟隨大陸做法：只有持健康碼的市民，才可進入商場食肆和乘搭公共交通工具。這消息流傳一段日子後，林鄭月娥終開腔澄清，說健康碼只為方便市民到廣東及澳門，若以此決定能否進出本地公眾地方，則「不切實際」，更指「有關建議混淆信息」。<br />\n<br />\n說到這裏，不得不又提一下「營銷大師」王亭之。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有王老前輩前車可鑒，你怎知道今天林鄭和建制派不是玩「左右互搏」？。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n若左右互搏奏效，下一招即登門坎效應（Foot-in-the-door technique）：先提出一個小請求，待對方執行後，再提出一個較大的請求，如是者逐級遞增。六十年代，心理學家Jonathan Freedman和Scott Fraser做了個實驗：先請求一群屋主，讓他們在窗戶貼小貼紙，宣傳安全駕駛，幾乎所有人都答允了；兩星期後，他們再要求同一批屋主，讓他們在草坪上豎立一塊又大又醜的告示牌。這個不合理的要求，結果也有76%屋主答應。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，另一群之前沒被要求貼小貼紙的屋主，僅有17%同意豎立那塊有礙觀瞻的告示牌。心理學家的解釋是：人總不自覺盼望自己一路走來，始終如一，既同意了某人較小的要求，若之後拒絕他另一個要求（哪怕是不合理的），就會感到「認知不協調」，而寧願調整自己去迎合別人。<br />\n<br />\n先用左右互搏讓大部分人接受方案B，接着用登門坎效應令很多人接納方案A，妙着！妙着！利申：我支持健康碼。"},{"pid":"f9edf75015a4f5bfca28838c3931b9e5ffed028c","tid":2171694,"uid":52056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"縮圖文字同內文不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縮圖講嘅係開天殺價落地還錢<br />\n<br />\n不過兩招都好陰險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a2a060c5870cca778efd7e4a890c4d4ff7ea7f","tid":2171694,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9edf75015a4f5bfca28838c3931b9e5ffed028c","tid":2171694,"uid":52056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"縮圖文字同內文不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縮圖講嘅係開天殺價落地還錢<br />\n<br />\n不過兩招都好陰險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"重睇最後一段唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba64d1c97f65057b09d27f79a06018e95bf40a1","tid":2171694,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:58:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9af761d89b3b74a8474d1b0c14d14baf8acbe809","tid":2171694,"uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19a2a060c5870cca778efd7e4a890c4d4ff7ea7f","tid":2171694,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9edf75015a4f5bfca28838c3931b9e5ffed028c","tid":2171694,"uid":52056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"縮圖文字同內文不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縮圖講嘅係開天殺價落地還錢<br />\n<br />\n不過兩招都好陰險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"重睇最後一段唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T0